metadata.name: Wisdomians #1
metadata.description: The Wisdomians NFT is a collection of 9,999 Wisdomians randomly generated on the blockchain. A high-utility project for people that strives for the best in every aspect of their lives takes their financial life and decisions seriously, and wants to enjoy life while being financially free. Holding this asset will give access and a major discount on the main project named ¨The Wisdomatic¨. Building trust and providing knowledge in the web3 world toward a community that is self-aware and is not afraid to break the mold of society to strive for greatness in their life.
